{"tid":1726446,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"死不瞑目的照片 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-11-16T07:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T08:28:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ef6dae436ea4000897ef8538d8325f321fd77de9","tid":1726446,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:11:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191116/20807132/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191116%2F20807132%2F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXgb0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=df539b11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191116%2F20807132%2F&h=4475a3f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191116/20807132/</a><br />\n<br />\n死不瞑目的照片 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191116/large/1573810573_6ad2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191116%2Flarge%2F1573810573_6ad2.jpg&h=631dd415&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n偶然有一宗「真正」自殺案，警謊記者會久旱逢甘地高調強調：有CCTV作證。荃灣一黑衣男子是單獨上樓自高處墮下死亡，並非坊間流傳的被斬、被警掟下樓、死後「被自殺」，或把已雪藏一段時間的僵硬屍體扔擲呀！「真的」滿地鮮血，警方呼冤：市民要看清楚事實，不關警方的事。<br />\n<br />\n一百宗（或數百、數千宗）警暴殺人、誤殺、延誤失救&hellip;&hellip;事件，只一宗正常，並不表示其他的「無可疑」，也不包括根本找不到失蹤者下落，可能被送中，可能鮮活壯健的年輕人內臟器官，正為病重的領導人權貴高幹富豪「享用」。<br />\n<br />\n作為傳媒人、寫作人，我看過的屍體照片也算多，且研究過死因和屍體實況──但，近幾個月來看過的，比過去加起來還多，且都拍得清晰特寫和死狀，初看很不安，漸漸習慣了，視感麻木但心情跌宕，被自殺的、被扔作浮屍的&hellip;&hellip;都有整合、認人、求報平安、追查。而太子站、新屋嶺、陳彥霖、周梓樂、各地獄私刑的警署&hellip;&hellip;CCTV仍有所遮瞞。<br />\n<br />\n逆權抗暴運動持續5個多月，離奇墮樓及浮屍「湧現」，大都死不瞑目。保安局局長李家超公公提供數據，只6~9月到院前死亡個案已2,537宗，比去年多，這些不尋常死亡的屍體待雪冤。別因一回無可疑便狡辯以偏概全。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"08536f67e3ad40c611d8c5699d79a8a5216f555e","tid":1726446,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:13:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">彥霖媽咪去咗邊？</span></span>"},{"pid":"0257eb5f54fa6d70f4ee51b13b8d291e53c4cd31","tid":1726446,"uid":207727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:17:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d7d964ff5ab8ae523f44dff55954ff4a50f1262","tid":1726446,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:18:24.000Z","msg":"[重推]全體和理非心聲: 係我哋做得吾夠, 感激前線所有<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726402\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726402</a>"},{"pid":"c8af64e224d881c798c9040ee725340c4edff1dc","tid":1726446,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:21:04.000Z","msg":"［區選］藍絲散水運動，正式開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1726325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1726325</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ad0758d9d455ca0f611865bc33b372cacb22edae","tid":1726446,"uid":299490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:25:45.000Z","msg":"1118-1122 黎明行動討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1726123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1726123</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當我地難得搵到真正春袋，亦連續數日行之有效時，叫休息叫停個班，對唔對得住周同學，荃灣警署被強姦少女，葵涌被殺手足，西灣河被槍擊手足同過去半年犧牲嘅其他同路人？"},{"pid":"aa0c9a4c949a8ca5da28cf386be9ef9ec9ad407a","tid":1726446,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08536f67e3ad40c611d8c5699d79a8a5216f555e","tid":1726446,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:13:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">彥霖媽咪去咗邊？</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:28:27.000Z","msg":"同緊黑警扑野，唔好阻我"}]}